50	    /// Compute a hash that summarizes all uncommitted changes in the working
51	    /// tree: staged changes, unstaged changes, and untracked files.
52	    /// Returns `None` for manual SCM mode, when the working tree is clean,
53	    /// or when a git command fails (errors are logged as warnings).
